<h1>What's Jobyssey all about?</h1>

<p>Jobyssey is a best match job search site.  When you upload your CV and tell us a bit about yourself we'll use that information to show you jobs that suit you best.  A little more about how Jobyssey works:</p>
  <ul>
  <li>Detailed skills profiles help emoployers understand you better.</li>
  <li>Work personality profiles let you find a position and company that suit how you like to work.</li>
  <li>Best match searching shows you the most suitable jobs first.</li>  
  <li>We keep your search confidential- you'll be known to employers by a code name until you agree to an interview.</li>
  <li>You'll be dealing directly with employers- no pressure from agencies or phantom jobs.</li>
  </ul>
  
